string: a guest of such high importance
a young man who , I believe , will soon become a part of the family
a most inconvenient sitting room for the evening
a prettyish kind of a little wilderness
a young woman of inferior birth
respectable , honourable , and ancient -- though untitled -- families
a young woman without family , connections , or fortune
the son of his late father 's steward
any person so wholly unconnected with me
